  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>IsSubmitted</TypeRef> method returns true if the batch has been submitted for processing.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[bool IsSubmitted() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="bool">
        True if the batch has already been submitted, false otherwise.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
